channel.title: Official release: SYNERGY-PKZ 317
channel.description:
[center] Well I decided to release this source (also under the influence of my other camaraderie's.) This source means the most to me when it comes to programming RSPS. A lot of hard work went through to make this source possible. We didn't plan to host it because I also got involved into more sophisticated projects. Please keep in mind
[size="5"]THERE IS AN ANTI-LEECH(ES)[/size] I mean what is the fun without it? :D.. Also that this is synergy-pkz 317 V1, there MAY be more releases in the future :).
PANELS?: :D
[IMG]http://i35.tinypic.com/2wfiemb.gif[/img]
DOWNLOAD: [b]LINK FIXED![/b http://www.mediafire.com/?kdukn5amm2n http://www.mediafire.com/?kdukn5amm2n http://www.mediafire.com/?kdukn5amm2n http://www.mediafire.com/?kdukn5amm2n
SERVER FEATURES -- -Animated GwD! -Anti-Dupe! -Anti-SYI + NULL! -Clan chat! -100% r'cbow emotes! -Defender emote! -Balanced XP rate! -Construction! -Member skillarea! -X-log disabled! -Pest control! -Fight pits! -Duel arena! -77+ commands! -Event server manager! -Sounds! -90% Godsword animations + specials! -Godsword special effects! -Funpk! -Custom interfaces! -3GB ram VPS! -'Attack' option in wildy only! -Great stability! -Vegeance emotes! -474 Whip emotes! -Stable -TWO iPanels! -Gadgets from ZombieSuite installed! -ConnectionFilter!

NOTE: REST OF PLAYER COMMANDS

AND THE REST OF THE OTHER COMMANDS ALSO![/spoiler]
